wdi2-SG.GEN.PARL.ZS.def: Women in parliaments are the percentage of parliamentary seats in a single or lower chamber held by women.
wdi2-SG.GEN.PARL.ZS.name: Proportion of seats held by women in national parliaments
wdi2-SG.GEN.PARL.ZS.source: Inter-Parliamentary Union (IPU) (www.ipu.org).  For the year of 1998, the data is as of August 10, 1998.
